# Industrial Applications by Unit and Topic

Here is the comprehensive list of Industrial Applications integrated into the CBSE Class X Mathematics curriculum applications, broken down by Unit and their respective sub-topics/components:

## Unit I: Number Systems
*   **General Unit Applications**: Cryptography (RSA Encryption), Digital Computing
*   **Contradiction Journey**: 📄 Why A4 Paper is Special
*   **Exploding Primes**: 🔐 Cryptography

## Unit II: Algebra
*   **General Unit Applications**: Finance & Economics, Physics & Ballistics, Chemical Engineering
*   **Arithmetic Progressions (AP Sums)**: 💰 Finance: Simple Interest
*   **Discriminant Visualizer**: ⚙️ Engineering Design
*   **Linear System Graph**: 🏭 Production Planning
*   **Parabola Graph**: 🚀 Projectile Motion
*   **Substitution Method**: 📦 Supply Chain Optimization
*   **Zeros & Coefficients**: 📡 Signal Processing

## Unit III: Coordinate Geometry
*   **General Unit Applications**: GPS & Navigation, Computer Graphics, Robotics
*   **Distance Formula**: 📡 GPS Navigation
*   **Section Formula**: 🖥️ Computer Graphics

## Unit IV: Geometry
*   **General Unit Applications**: Architecture & Construction, Optics & Lenses, Art & Perspective
*   **AAA Similarity**: 🎥 Computer Graphics
*   **BPT Visualizer**: 📐 Civil Engineering
*   **SAS Similarity**: ✈️ Aerospace Engineering
*   **SSS Similarity**: 🏗️ Structural Engineering
*   **Tangents to a Circle**: 👓 Optics & Lenses
*   **Tangents from an External Point**: 📡 Telecommunications
*   **Triangle Similarity**: 🏛️ Architecture

## Unit V: Trigonometry
*   **General Unit Applications**: Aviation & Navigation, Oceanography, Astronomy
*   **Heights & Distances**: ✈️ Navigation
*   **Pythagorean Identity**: 📡 Signal Processing
*   **Special Angles**: 🏛️ Architecture
*   **Trigonometric Identities**: 🎵 Audio Engineering
*   **Trigonometric Ratios**: 🏗️ Construction
*   **Trigonometric Relationships**: ⚡ Electrical Engineering

## Unit VI: Mensuration
*   **General Unit Applications**: Packaging & Manufacturing, HVAC & Architecture, Medicine
*   **Sector Area**: 🍕 Food Industry
*   **Segment Area**: 🌉 Civil Engineering
*   **Solid Lab**: 🏭 Manufacturing

## Unit VII: Statistics & Probability
*   **General Unit Applications**: Quality Control (Six Sigma), Insurance (Actuarial Science), AI & Machine Learning
*   **Mean Methods**: 📈 Market Research
*   **Probability**: ☂️ Insurance
*   **Statistics**: 📊 Data Science
